    ------
    Installation
    ------
    ------

Installation

    * Define the env var $HBQL_HOME and unzip the distribution to $HBQL_HOME.

    * Add the hbql.jar and the jars in $HBQL_HOME/lib directory to your classpath.

    * To verify your installation, run the {{{console.html}console}} and enter the {{{statements/version.html}version}}
     command.


